---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Bird Friendly Waterloo — Getting Started">
  <Header slot="header" currentPath="/waterloo" />

  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Bird Friendly Waterloo</h1>
      <span class="status status-in-progress">◌ Getting Started</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="page-content">
    <p>
      The City of Waterloo is embarking on its journey toward
      <strong>Bird Friendly City</strong> certification from
      <a href="https://naturecanada.ca/defend-nature/how-you-help-us-take-action/bfc/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nature Canada</a>.
    </p>

    <p>
      As an official subcommittee of
      <a href="https://www.waterlooregionnature.ca" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Waterloo Region Nature</a>,
      we are building a team of community members committed to making Waterloo a safer place for birds.
      We meet regularly and work cooperatively with the City of Waterloo and other community organizations.
    </p>

    <p>
      Inspired by Kitchener's successful certification in 2024, we are developing an action plan
      to address threats to birds, protect and restore habitats, and engage residents across the city.
    </p>

    <p>
      <strong>Interested in joining?</strong> We're looking for passionate community members to help
      Waterloo achieve Bird Friendly City status. Stay tuned for more details.
    </p>

    <a href="/" class="back-link">← Back to home</a>
  </div>

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</BaseLayout>
